                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1" defective="false">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus/>justify"&gt;Fol. 253va:   ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተጽሕፈት፡ በ፫፻ወ፯፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ዘአጽሐፋ፡ እንዘ፡ ሹም፡ ወረድ፡ በዘመነ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለንግሥነ፡ በካፋ፡ ወጳጳስነ፡ አባ፡ ክርስተ፡ ዱወሉ፡ ለመቅደሰ፡&lt;...&gt;፡[fol. 253vb] ሰበር፨ ወእመሂቦ፡&lt;...&gt;፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ወአሜን፨A part of the colophon has been erased. The date mentioned is 307 year of mercy (= 1731 A.D.); the colophon refers to the donor šum Wäräd, King Bäkaffa (r. 1721-30) and Metropolitan Krǝstodolu (III) (in tenure 1720-35). Their names have been written over erasures.</colophon>
                  </msItem>
